    // How does it work
    .howwork(style="margin: 20px auto; width: 90%; background-color: #5970C3; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; position: relative;")
      h2(style="font-size: 4rem; text-align: center; color: white;") How does it work?
      p(style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: white;") 
        | 1. For the residents:
        br
        | Users use CAYZ to set up and manage their security code.
        br
        | Residents can also create code for visitors.
        br
        | 2. For security:
        br
        | The security team has access to the system to legally secure every resident.
        br
        | They can initiate alerts to quickly respond to security incidents.
        br
        | &nbsp;
      .button-container(style="position: absolute; bottom: 20px; right: 50px;")
